To install this package, you will need

   *) the SCons build system (http://www.scons.org/);
   *) the Boost C++ utility library (http://www.boost.org/); and
   *) the TCLAP C++ command line parser library (http://tclap.sourceforge.net/).

To build the package, type

   scons

To install the package (by default into /usr/local), type

   scons install

If you want to build the randomized test suite, type

   scons test
